void reverseInPlace<T>(List<T> list) {
  int left = 0;
  int right = list.length - 1;

  while (left < right) {
    // Swap elements
    T temp = list[left];
    list[left] = list[right];
    list[right] = temp;

    left++;
    right--;
  }
}

// Usage
var numbers = [1, 2, 3, 4, 5];
reverseInPlace(numbers);
print(numbers); // [5, 4, 3, 2, 1]
```

**Time Complexity**: O(n/2) = O(n)
**Space Complexity**: O(1)

